      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 4 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[6 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[8 tbsp] </span><strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated chicken</strong> and cook for 5 min on each side, or until nicely golden, crisp and cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Once done, transfer the <strong>golden</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> to a plate covered with kitchen paper<strong> </strong>and set aside for later</p>",
