    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>,<strong> </strong>pat it dry with kitchen paper then slice into wedges</p><p>Chop your<strong> chives</strong> finely, then peel and grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong>, <strong>Dijon mustard</strong>, <strong>grated garlic </strong>(not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) and <strong>chopped chives</strong> in a bowl</p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>ranch dip</strong></p>",
